---
import BgGrid from "@/components/assets/BgGrid.astro";
---

<section id="case-study" class="border-b border-white/10 bg-[#0a0a0a] overflow-hidden divide-y divide-white/10">
  <div class="p-8 md:p-16 relative">
    <BgGrid />
    <div class="relative">
      <p class="text-[#ff5f1f] font-mono text-[10px] mb-4 tracking-[0.4em] uppercase opacity-60">
        // Featured Architecture
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-white text-4xl md:text-7xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter leading-none">
        CVE-RSS <span class="text-white/20">ALERT SYSTEM.</span>
      </h2>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 divide-y lg:divide-y-0 lg:divide-x divide-white/10">
    <div class="lg:col-span-7 p-8 md:p-16">
      
      {/* Problem Analysis */}
      <div class="mb-20">
        <h3 class="text-white text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 bg-[#ff5f1f]"></span> Problem Analysis
        </h3>
        <p class="text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-6 font-light">
          Security teams face "Alert Fatigue" from manual monitoring of NVD and CISA databases. Manually parsing RSS feeds results in a <strong class="text-white">4-6 hour delay</strong> between vulnerability publication and internal triage, leaving a critical window open for exploitation.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <span class="px-3 py-1 border border-white/10 text-white/40 text-[9px] uppercase font-mono tracking-widest">Slow Response</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 border border-white/10 text-white/40 text-[9px] uppercase font-mono tracking-widest">Manual Triage</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Solution Design */}
      <div class="mb-20">
        <h3 class="text-white text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 bg-[#ff5f1f]"></span> Solution Design
        </h3>
        <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-8">
          I designed an event-driven pipeline using <strong class="text-white">n8n</strong> to automate the entire lifecycle of a vulnerability. The system architecture includes:
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          {[
            { label: "CISA/NVD Ingestion", desc: "Real-time polling via RSS and REST API." },
            { label: "State Management", desc: "Google Sheets acts as a lightweight DB to track 'Seen' CVEs and prevent alert duplication." },
            { label: "Dynamic Risk Scoring", desc: "Custom JS node to parse multi-version CVSS (3.1, 3.0, 2.0) and route by severity." }
          ].map(item => (
            <div class="group p-4 border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] hover:border-[#ff5f1f]/20 transition-colors">
               <p class="text-[#ff5f1f] font-mono text-[10px] uppercase mb-1">{item.label}</p>
               <p class="text-white/40 text-sm font-light italic">{item.desc}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Stack & Metrics Grid */}
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 pt-12 border-t border-white/5">
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-white/20 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">Technical Stack</h4>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {["n8n", "NVD API v2.0", "Regex", "Javascript", "Google Sheets", "Gmail"].map(tech => (
              <span class="text-[9px] font-mono text-white/40 border border-white/10 px-3 py-1 bg-white/5 uppercase">{tech}</span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-white/20 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">Impact Metrics</h4>
          <ul class="text-white font-mono text-xs space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 font-bold"><span class="text-[#ff5f1f]">+</span> 95% REDUCTION IN TRIAGE TIME</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 font-bold"><span class="text-[#ff5f1f]">+</span> ZERO DUPLICATED ALERTS</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 font-bold"><span class="text-[#ff5f1f]">+</span> INSTANT CRITICAL NOTIFICATION</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="lg:col-span-5 bg-white/[0.01] p-8 md:p-16 flex flex-col divide-y divide-white/5">
      
      {/* Code Snippet Card */}
      <div class="pb-16">
        <div class="border border-white/10 bg-black/40 backdrop-blur-sm relative rounded-sm overflow-hidden">
          <div class="bg-[#ff5f1f] text-black text-[9px] font-black px-3 py-1 uppercase tracking-tighter">
          </div>
          <pre class="p-6 text-[11px] leading-relaxed text-white/50 overflow-x-auto font-